ongoing cost.</p>\n<p>\n	You can purchase a 10Layer licence outright, or pay it off over a year for a small premium. Alternatively, we can include it in the cost of hosting in a software-as-a-service model.</p>\n<p>\n	The cost of a commecial licence is $50,000, with a cost of $5,000 per additional website.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	Please contact us at <a href=\"mailto:info@10layer.com?subject=Please%20contact%20me%20about%20a%2010Layer%20licence\">info@10layer.com</a>&nbsp;or one of our <a href=\"/page/team\">team</a> to discuss a comprehensive quote.</p>\n');
